The foregoing aspects and many of the attendant advantages of this invention will become more readily appreciated as the same become better understood by reference to the following detailed description, when taken in conjunction with the accompanying drawings, wherein:


FIG. 1 illustrates an elevated perspective view of a dual-adjustable belt idler of the present invention, configured for use with a single belt;


FIG. 2 illustrates an exploded perspective view of the dual-adjustable belt idler of FIG. 1;


FIG. 3 illustrates an elevated perspective view of an alternate dual-adjustable belt idler of the present invention, configured for use with two belts;


FIG. 4 illustrates a side view of the dual-adjustable belt idler of FIG. 3;


FIG. 5 illustrates an exploded perspective view of another alternate dual-adjustable belt idler of the present invention that includes intermediate contact rollers and shows interwoven tensioning of a double-V drive belt; and


FIG. 6 illustrates an exploded perspective view of the dual-adjustable belt idler of FIG. 5, and shows non-interwoven tensioning of a flat drive belt.
